    DefineBitsJPEG3Tag

    public class DefineBitsJPEG2Tag
extends DefineBitsTag
    Represents a DefineBitsJPEG2 tag in a SWF file.

    This tag defines a bitmap character with JPEG compression. It differs from DefineBitsTag in that it contains both the JPEG encoding table and the JPEG image data. This tag allows multiple JPEG images with differing encoding tables to be defined within a single SWF file.
